e" align="left" title="Reduce Stress" el_class="small-text-icon stress-ic benefits-ic" title_color="#676767" text_color="#676767"]The phytonutrients and probiotics make sure your hormones are at the right level, which in turn reduces the stress[/vsc-text-icon][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" vsc_parallax="yes" vsc_id="feedback" vsc_padding_top="15" css=".vc_custom_1478782459753{padding-top: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;}" el_class="slide2"][vc_column vsc_animation="fade-in" vsc_duration=".5" css=".vc_custom_1477567181909{margin-bottom: 2% !important;}"][vc_row_inner el_class="maintain-healthy"][vc_column_inner width="5/12"][vc_empty_space height="60px" el_class="slide2_img"][vc_single_image image="5369" alignment="center" img_size="large"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="7/12"][vc_empty_space height="40px"][vsc-section-title align="left" size="small" title="Maintain a Healthy LIfestyle Easily with Daily Greens" title_color="#b4cc1a" subtitle_color="#676767"][/vsc-section-title][vc_separator][vc_column_text]
<p style="text-align: left;">Our famous Daily Greens formula contains herbs that have been known to strengthen &amp; rejuvenate the body for centuries.</p>
&nbsp;
<p style="text-align: left;">With its high vitamin &amp; mineral content, it gives sustainable energy and is a great replacement to any ‘multivitamin’. These herbs have been treasured throughout the years for their high concentrations of Vitamins A, C, B, B12, D, E and K, as well as enzymes, chlorophyll and trace minerals.</p>
&nbsp;
<p style="text-align: left;">One scoop, once a day of Amazing Greens will help give you virtually every vital nutrient your body needs. Each delicious serving delivers vegetables, phytonutrients, probiotics, digestive enzymes, fiber, herbs, to help you feel healthier. Daily Greens can really make a difference.</p>
&nbsp;
<p style="text-align: left;">Prepare to feel your body like never before. For only 30 days you feel the outstanding effects</p>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row vsc_no_mb="no-margin" css=".vc_custom_1478842970456{padding-top: 15px !important;}" vsc_id="about" el_class="row-with-only"][vc_column el_align="alignright" vsc_animation="slide-to-right" vsc_duration=".5" css=".vc_custom_1477565867286{margin-top: 2% !important;padding-top: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;}"][vsc-section-title align="center" size="small" title="With only 2 capsules a day you can have the green's best nutritions" title_color="#b4cc1a" subtitle_color="#676767"][/vsc-section-title][vc_separator][/vc_column][vc_column el_class="group-inside-dg"][vc_row_inner vsc_bg_size="auto" vsc_bg_image="5295" el_class="row-inside-dg"][vc_column_inner el_align="alignleft" width="5/12"][vsc-text-icon media_type="img-type" align="left" title="Young Barley Grass" el_class="young_barley-ic ingredients-ic"]The juice of barley grass contains beta carotene, vitamins B1, B2, B6, B12, pantothenic acid, and folic acid. Minerals present include potassium, calcium, iron, phosphorus, and magnesium. Other constituents are chlorophyll, amino acids, protein, fiber, and enzymes.[/vsc-text-icon][vsc-text-icon media_type="img-type" align="left" title="Wheat Grass" el_class="wheat_grass-ic ingredients-ic"]Wheatgrass juice is an effective healer because it contains all minerals known to man, and vitamins A, B-complex, C, E, l and K. It is extremely rich in protein, and contains 17 amino acids, the building blocks of protein. 3. Wheatgrass juice contains up to 70% chlorophyll, which is an important blood builder[/vsc-text-icon][vsc-text-icon media_type="img-type" align="left" title="Bee Pollen" el_class="bee_pollen-ic ingredients-ic"]Bee pollen is the food of the young bee and it is approximately 40% protein. It is considered one of nature’s most completely nourishing foods. It contains nearly all nutrients required by humans. About half of its protein is in the form of free amino acids that are ready to be used directly by the body.[/vsc-text-icon][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_align="alignright" width="1/6"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="5/12"][vsc-text-icon media_type="img-type" align="left" title="Spirulina" el_class="spirulina-ic ingredients-ic"]Many studies promote spirulina as a treatment for a range of metabolism and heart health issues, including weight loss, diabetes and high cholesterol. It is also recommended as an aid for various mental and emotional disorders, including anxiety, stress, depression and attention deficit-hyperactivity disorder (ADHD)[/vsc-text-icon][vsc-text-icon media_type="img-type" align="left" title="Alfalfa Leaf" el_class="alfalfa-ic ingredients-ic"]Alfalfa leaf contains essential vitamins including the entire spectrum of B-vitamins, A, D, E and K. Alfalfa Leaf is a source of iron, niacin, biotin, folic acid, calcium, magnesium, phosphorous and potassium[/vsc-text-icon][vsc-text-icon media_type="img-type" align="left" title="Royal Jelly" el_class="royal_jelly-ic ingredients-ic"]Royal jelly is used for asthma, hay fever, liver disease, pancreatitis, sleep troubles (insomnia), premenstrual syndrome (PMS), stomach ulcers, kidney disease, bone fractures, menopausal symptoms, skin disorders, and high cholesterol[/vsc-text-icon][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vsc-button text="Learn more" align="center" text_size="14" color="#b4cc1a" url="https://behealthy.today/the-daily-greens-nutrients/" el_class="btn-narrow"][vc_empty_space][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" vsc_text_scheme="darker-overlay" vsc_id="feedback" vsc_padding_top="15" css=".vc_custom_1478863194224{padding-top: 24px !important;padding-bottom: 24px !important;background-color: #f6f6f6 !important;}" el_class="parent-one-scoop"][vc_column width="1/12" vsc_animation="fade-in" vsc_duration=".5"][/vc_column][vc_column el_class="dg-one-scoop" width="1/2"][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vsc-section-title title="Daily Green" title_color="